content: 2014 Chinese film ***Nature Law*** or ***Break*** ([Chinese](/wiki/Simplified_Chinese_characters): 拆散专家) is a 2014 Chinese-Singaporean [romantic comedy](/wiki/Romantic_comedy) film directed by Li Jian and Qiu Zhongwei. It was released on November 7. ## Cast - [Eva Huang](/wiki/Eva_Huang) - Jia Yiping - [Johnny Zhang](/wiki/Johnny_Zhang) - Liu Tianzuo - [Lam Suet](/wiki/Lam_Suet) - Xiao Jian - Jiang Hongbo - Liu Huan - Yue Yueli - [Li Jing](/wiki/Li_Jing_(actor)) ## Reception By November 7, the film had earned [¥](/wiki/Chinese_yuan)1.03 million at the Chinese box office.
